title: Hour 2 - Julio Jones to Tampa, Ross Tucker
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Julio Jones to Tampa, Ross Tucker
description:
Dan reminds us that Julio Jones isn't the receiver he once was as he signs with Tom Brady and the Buccaneers. He talks to Ross Tucker about that and the rest of the NFL story lines as camps open up around the league.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
